===Preposition===
'''despite'''
# [[in spite of]]
:'''Quotations'''
:* '''1592&ndash;1609''': So thou through windows of thine age shall see / '''Despite''' of wrinkles this thy golden time. &mdash; William Shakespeare, Sonnet III
:* '''1592&ndash;1609''': Yet, do thy worst, old Time: '''despite''' thy wrong, / My love shall in my verse ever live young. mdash; William Shakespeare, Sonnet XIX

